{"tid":1548674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話自己去澳門大澳昂坪咩都好啦 總之唔好整假機票","createTime":"2019-09-07T05:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:28:58.000Z","uid":36115,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e54bca0dcf51fbace1a38a084f7e9d3547a4d14","tid":1548674,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"搭A車既話自己去澳門 佢都吹你唔漲<br />\n搭E車既話去東涌轉巴士去大澳昂坪都得<br />\n<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整假機票係犯法</span></span><br />\n狗狗要check機票真定假好簡單<br />\n有你個booking reference或者機票號碼已經睇到係咪真係有呢張機票存在<br />\n如果佢一懷疑你 check到係冇就已經干犯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偽造文書</span></span><br />\n即刻拉得你<br />\n<br />\n仲有巴打教人整假機票都要小心<br />\n有可能告你<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">教唆他人行使偽造文書</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以大家有千千萬萬個理由入大嶼山<br />\n唔使用d咁高風險既方法<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Mon Po狗死全家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9dac1de8042e5b5a971a0c342a685be636a734eb","tid":1548674,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b81e868141ae135c90acf31e4799a95bff0f075b","tid":1548674,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"822e521a95579b0e00e3832a146361206b306016","tid":1548674,"uid":290624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"b7cf8ad1be195e0bcb26d5a2becad0bdd81b0e2f","tid":1548674,"uid":36115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"